&lt;p&gt;We are actively looking for professionals in the following areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agile Transformation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cloud and Technology Strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DevOps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solution Design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;App Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate’s experience may include but is not limited to the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge and experience in one or more Cloud platforms (AWS, Microsoft Azure, Google Cloud, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge and experience in one or more database platforms (i.e. SQL, DB2, Oracle, Postgres, MySQL, NoSQL, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
